![120.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1585755759837-99KT57BZYKVZ3D1Y56CH/120.jpg)

After less than a month, [**Bloodshot**](https://www.sonypictures.com/movies/bloodshot) is available on streaming services and might be the last theatrical release for a comic book film in a long while. Based on the Valiant's comics character of the same name, Bloodshot starring Vin Diesel deals with a seemingly unstoppable soldier, brought back from the dead using nanotechnology and what that means for his enemies. Full of action and a bit of a throwback, does Vin Diesel's Bloodshot have what it takes to stand toe to toe with other comic book movie heroes? You have to listen to find out!  
   
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](/comicbookclique/episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
